{"tid":1800722,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"達粉時代","createTime":"2019-12-28T05:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T07:22:16.000Z","uid":218659,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1b0f1ecfbd4013114ae3fc9c326f01119f2aa6","tid":1800722,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"你和誰結伴前來 是否俾我apple <br />\n自從錢愛到現在 是哪款Apple watch呀<br />\n你回來你應回來 達粉需要未來<br />\n但仍然值得去看 沒錯過直播再睇翻<br />\n<br />\n達哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ef9b21cf0ca7a27e669e7282dd050ae1b326ff","tid":1800722,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"（聯署）你班友快Ｄ同我簽晒佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799015</a>"},{"pid":"f6792750cd4d99814e87f7db3358e6238c0c678f","tid":1800722,"uid":218659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"六月，對達哥感到失望。<br />\n七月，對達哥感到憤怒。<br />\n八月，對達哥感到可惜。<br />\n九月，些少懷念每晚睇開台既日子。<br />\n十月，開始睇番達哥每晚既重播。<br />\n十一月，很想念他。<br />\n十二月了，默默為達哥打氣"},{"pid":"2f6a0d3d39f17c9a516c288ab7f30c1daa7e8403","tid":1800722,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"樓主好能25 收完達哥Apple watch仲敢反達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc78c5959b42ae588d6b06968de0fdaa7794ad3e","tid":1800722,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"以為講緊韋達"},{"pid":"257ae70685bf2122a8b8aa3aacde1df2e4292aca","tid":1800722,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:49:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"9badb15c1ab20a6b8eaa05891ef90c50e6e6a61c","tid":1800722,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6a0d3d39f17c9a516c288ab7